---
title: BBQ Sausage Meatballs with Smashed Potatoes and Garlicky Sugar Snap Peas
description: These tasty meatballs are flavoured with BBQ spices and garlic, tossed in a tangy BBQ sauce and sprinkled with chives. It's a comfort-food classic you'll enjoy any night of the week.
